== English ==

=== Noun ===
'''electrocardiograph'''
# A [[device]] used in the [[diagnosis]] and [[detection]] of [[heart]] [[abnormalities]] that [[measure]]s [[electric]] [[potential]]s on the [[surface]] of the [[body]] and creates a record ([[electrocardiogram]]) of the electrical currents associated with heart muscle activity
